---
import FoodServiceLayout from "./FoodServiceLayout.astro";
import beefRavioliImage from "../../../assets/images/perth-food-photography/Beef-Check-Ravioli_01-scaled.jpg";
---

<FoodServiceLayout
  imageSrc={beefRavioliImage}
  imageAlt="Perth restaurant food photography – plated beef ravioli dish"
>
  <div class="food-service__heading">
    <span class="food-service__eyebrow">FOOD PHOTOGRAPHY FOR</span>
    <span class="food-service__title">RESTAURANTS &amp; CAFÉS</span>
  </div>

  <div class="food-service__copy">
    <p>
      Don’t let bland photos hurt your business.
      <strong>
        If your menu, website, Google Business Profile or delivery platforms
        like Uber Eats and DoorDash are relying on low-quality images, you’re
        leaving sales on the table.
      </strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      Stunning, mouth-watering imagery is an art form and a crucial part of
      making your venue a must-visit. 
      <strong>
        We create premium food photography for Perth restaurants, cafés, bars
        and food trucks – from hero dishes to full-table spreads and interior
        lifestyle shots.
      </strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Visually captivating stories:</strong>
      We photograph plated dishes, ingredients, chefs, staff and your venue so
      diners can experience your atmosphere before they ever walk in. Every
      image is crafted to look great across menus, websites and social media.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Stress-free shoot:</strong>
      We work around your service times, bring professional lighting and guide
      you through the process so your team can focus on what they do best –
      creating incredible food – while we capture imagery that drives bookings
      and online orders.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a href="/contact/" class="food-service__button">
    CONTACT
  </a>
</FoodServiceLayout>
